<section id="about" class="about">
    <h2>About MERCATO</h2>
    <p>
        MERCATO was inspired by the vibrant local markets in Rwanda. Having grown up surrounded by these markets, I wanted to bring that experience to the digital world.
        The goal is to make local Rwandan marketplaces accessible to everyone. MERCATO is a part of my Portfolio Project for Holberton School.
    </p>
